edu.stanford.ramcloud.multiop

Class MultiOpObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.stanford.ramcloud.RAMCloudObject
      • edu.stanford.ramcloud.multiop.MultiOpObject
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    MultiReadObject, MultiRemoveObject, MultiWriteObject

    public abstract class MultiOpObject
extends RAMCloudObject
    RAMCloudObject returned from multi-op operations. Holds a status code for the status of this operation.
